{"word":"ἕως","slug":"ἕως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἕως</el></b> [complex origin] marker of limit<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> as temporal marker<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> conjunctive use <b>till, until <a href='B:470 2:9'>Mt 2:9</a>, <a href='B:470 2:13'>13</a>; <a href='B:470 12:20'>12:20</a>; <a href='B:470 16:28'>16:28</a>; <a href='B:470 24:39'>24:39</a>; <a href='B:480 6:10'>Mk 6:10</a>; <a href='B:490 9:27'>Lk 9:27</a>; <a href='B:490 17:8'>17:8</a>; <a href='B:500 21:22'>J 21:22</a>; <a href='B:510 2:35'>Ac 2:35</a>; <a href='B:530 4:5'>1 Cor 4:5</a>; <a href='B:600 2:7'>2 Th 2:7</a>; <a href='B:610 4:13'>1 Ti 4:13</a>; <a href='B:650 1:13'>Hb 1:13</a>; <a href='B:650 10:13'>10:13</a>; <a href='B:660 5:7'>Js 5:7</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> as long as, while <a href='B:480 6:45'>Mk 6:45</a>; <a href='B:500 9:4'>J 9:4</a>; <a href='B:500 12:35'>J 12:35</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as terminal marker, a usage (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ funct.\">funct.</a> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a>), developed since Aristotle:<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of position or place <b>as far as, to <a href='B:470 11:23'>Mt 11:23</a>; <a href='B:490 2:15'>Lk 2:15</a>; <a href='B:490 4:29'>4:29</a>; <a href='B:490 24:50'>24:50</a></b> (with <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a></el>); <b><a href='B:510 1:8'>Ac 1:8</a>; <a href='B:510 11:19'>11:19</a>, <a href='B:510 11:22'>22</a>; <a href='B:540 12:2'>2 Cor 12:2</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔσω\">ἔσω</a></el> right into <b><a href='B:480 14:54'>Mk 14:54</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνω\">ἄνω</a></el> to the top/brim <b><a href='B:500 2:7'>J 2:7</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a></el> close to <b><a href='B:490 24:50'>Lk 24:50</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κάτω\">κάτω</a></el> to bottom <b><a href='B:470 27:51'>Mt 27:51</a>.</b> In extended scaled sense: <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπὸ\">ἀπὸ</a> μιϰροῦ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> μεγάλου</el> from small to great <b><a href='B:650 8:11'>Hb 8:11</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἑπτάκις\">ἑπτάκις</a></el> as many as seven times <b><a href='B:470 18:21'>Mt 18:21f</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> ἡμίσους</el> up to the half <b><a href='B:480 6:23'>Mk 6:23</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a> ἔστιν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> ἑνός</el> there is not even one <b><a href='B:520 3:12'>Ro 3:12</a>;</b> <el>ἐᾶτε <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> τούτου</el> enough of this <b><a href='B:490 22:51'>Lk 22:51</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of time or calendric moment <b>until <a href='B:470 27:64'>Mt 27:64</a>; <a href='B:480 14:25'>Mk 14:25</a>; <a href='B:490 1:80'>Lk 1:80</a>; <a href='B:490 23:44'>23:44</a>; <a href='B:510 1:22'>Ac 1:22</a>; <a href='B:510 19:9'>19:9</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:530 1:8'>1 Cor 1:8</a>; <a href='B:540 1:13'>2 Cor 1:13</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὗ\">οὗ</a></el> until <b><a href='B:470 18:34'>Mt 18:34</a>; <a href='B:490 13:21'>Lk 13:21</a>; <a href='B:490 22:18'>22:18</a>; <a href='B:510 21:26'>Ac 21:26</a>; <a href='B:510 25:21'>25:21</a>.</b> Of a terminal point conceived temporally <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> ϑερισμοῦ</el> <b><a href='B:470 13:30'>Mt 13:30</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> ϑανάτου</el> <b><a href='B:470 26:38'>26:38</a>; <a href='B:480 14:34'>Mk 14:34</a>.</b> Adv. phrase <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄρτι\">ἄρτι</a></el> until now <b><a href='B:470 11:12'>Mt 11:12</a>; <a href='B:500 2:10'>J 2:10</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> τοῦ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νῦν\">νῦν</a></el> until now <b><a href='B:470 24:21'>Mt 24:21</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πότε\">πότε</a></el> how long <b><a href='B:470 17:17'>17:17</a>; <a href='B:500 10:24'>J 10:24</a>; <a href='B:730 6:10'>Rv 6:10</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἕως\">ἕως</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σήμερον\">σήμερον</a></el> to this very day <b><a href='B:540 3:15'>2 Cor 3:15</a>.</b> —W. pronoun of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or proper name <b>(up) to, until <a href='B:470 1:17'>Mt 1:17</a>; <a href='B:470 11:13'>11:13</a>; <a href='B:490 4:42'>Lk 4:42</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἑώρακα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Ϛ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}